headline: California American Water Rings in the New Year with Reminders and Resolutions for Water Services
summary: SAN DIEGO, January 07, 2025--California American Water, is here to help you ring in the new year with reminders and resolutions for saving water and money.

headline: American Water Rings in the New Year with Reminders and Resolutions for Water Services
summary: CAMDEN, N.J., January 07, 2025--American Water (NYSE: AWK), the largest regulated water and wastewater utility company in the U.S., is here to help customers and the general public ring in the new year with reminders and resolutions for saving water and money.
